snakes and ladder
there is a board (nxN)which has snakes and ladders which has from and to cell position
there are n players which can play this game
there is a dice which rolls and player has to move that steps on board
can a player be assigned with piece and a player can have multiple pieces
only human players
rules for starting a game --->1 or 6(max no of dice)
one dice but in future we can have multiple dice
winning game--> who reaches the end of board first all piece of that person
if n-1 player reaches the end then game will only stop.
leader board where each player ranking will be shown
